Description.Chinese:
与投资者一起建造帝国大教堂,需要满足所有公共服务的需要。
大部分来自Fishboss Old-Town mod，所以与它不兼容。

Build the imperial cathedral with investors.
Fullfills the needs of all public services.
Mostly taken from Fishboss Old-Town mod, so incompatible with it.
